This 14mm female quartz e-banger fits 14mm male joints on your bubbler pipe or dab rig, and a 20mm enail heater coil. Get the most from your wax by pairing this quartz nail with a carb cap dabber tool to cool the vapor and let you savor the tasty terpenes. Hook it up to an enail and adjust the temperature as desired. The convenience of stable and predictable temperatures without the hassles of a torch!
